"title": "5317: foundation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5317",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The solid base on which a secure structure may be built; used chiefly for the base of the temple. It is used figuratively of Jesus Christ and the apostles and prophets as the secure foundation on which the church is built. Obedience to the teaching of Jesus Christ is the true foundation of Christian living.</p>\n<h2>The place of foundations in building</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:17\">1KI 5:17</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:26\">JOS 6:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:34\">1KI 16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:37\">1KI 6:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:10\">1KI 7:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:3\">2CH 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:16\">2CH 8:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:3\">EZR 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:11-Ezra3:12\">EZR 3:11–3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:12\">EZR 4:12</a> <em>restoring the walls of Jerusalem</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:16\">EZR 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:3\">EZR 6:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:19\">JOB 4:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:28\">ISA 44:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:8\">EZK 41:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:18\">HAG 2:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:9\">ZEC 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:9\">ZEC 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:26\">ACT 16:26</a></p>\n<h2>Destruction of foundations is an indication of divine judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:11\">LAM 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:22\">DEU 32:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:16\">2SA 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:25-Jer51:26\">JER 51:25–51:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:14\">EZK 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:4\">EZK 30:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:6\">MIC 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The foundation of the church</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:11\">1CO 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a></p>\n<h3>The apostles and prophets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:20\">ROM 15:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:10\">1CO 3:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:20\">EPH 2:19–2:20</a></p>\n<h2>The church as the foundation of God's truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:14-1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:14–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:19\">2TI 2:19</a></p>\n<h2>Obedience as a secure foundation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:46-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:46–6:49</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:15-Job22:18\">JOB 22:15–22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:12-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:12–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:18–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>The foundation of the earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25\">PSA 102:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1SA 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4\">JOB 38:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:7\">PSA 18:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:15\">PSA 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1-Ps24:2\">PSA 24:1–24:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:5\">PSA 82:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:31\">PRO 8:22–8:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:13\">ISA 48:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:13\">ISA 51:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:16\">ISA 51:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:2\">MIC 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:1\">ZEC 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:10\">HEB 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The foundations of the city of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:10\">HEB 11:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:14\">REV 21:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:19\">REV 21:19</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of foundation</h2>\n<h3>God himself as the foundation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:5-Isa33:6\">ISA 33:5–33:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The foundation of God's throne</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:14\">PSA 89:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:2\">PSA 97:2</a></p>\n<h2>The need for a firm foundation in the Christian life</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:19–2:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1-Heb6:2\">HEB 6:1–6:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:4–2:5</a></p>",
